platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love rediscovering hedgehog history with this enhanced edition of one of Sonics greatest adventures. This game sizzles with all the sprawling levels and blazing speed you remember from the 90s, but this classic platformer is better than ever on the App Store. With crisp widescreen graphics, tight controls, and awesome extra content, its just a blast.
